{"id": "a07a223d3d7dfb20b88266f49e68f5a7ac5319d11f8309b17ea86a2789666073", "item_id": "993b875a81:0", "text": "Mixes two colors together according to the specified mix percentage. The mixed color result is calculated as:"}
{"id": "571461f36f3a202669eabf3896a7faa519b66ff6d8409bf36641f4e8cdf21c2e", "item_id": "993b875a81:3", "text": "Color 1"}
{"id": "0fa6eebbde817d038298c17dd381f6c32ebd9965b2d89b5292be72114d67cc42", "item_id": "993b875a81:8", "text": "The first color that is mixed with the second color."}
{"id": "ef792d28787255b4be2418a926aae2906bef2b7b175b76b6dbfc91b1c7974ea0", "item_id": "993b875a81:5", "text": "Color 2"}
{"id": "8e52cdb8186f6bcaf81a332f5314f872445bd482fbadf8f71b29f4bd3542af26", "item_id": "993b875a81:6", "text": "The second color that is mixed with the first color."}
{"id": "8ae012d51747c9a3e51613b1ba8305b377fcada7de30e2b7156d51c19f0b89e0", "item_id": "993b875a81:7", "text": "Mixer"}
{"id": "6f10f38bd0b7d722478807d683aeb4f1309da6ce87bc05d5e5d6700b8b27ed12", "item_id": "993b875a81:9", "text": "Clamp Mixer"}
{"id": "736cc5604a1ae95a212a8602af62f09d2cfaecd25593eba79290834e3d3a4323", "item_id": "993b875a81:10", "text": "Keep the mix value between 0 and 1 to make sure you only get either color1 or color2 when outside of that range."}
